<L>ffor drede of Ialowsie mennys apperceyuynges</L>
<L>No man but launcelett and he is dede</L>
<L N="288">&thorn;erfor I passe ouer of al &thorn;is lustihede
<PB REF="00000255.tif" N="225"><MILESTONE UNIT="6-text p" N="487"></L>
