<L>&thorn;e Spices and &thorn;e wyne is come an&omacr;n</L>
<L>Thei ete and drinke and whan &thorn;is had an ende<MILESTONE N="107b" UNIT="folio"></L>
<L N="296">Vnto &thorn;e temple as reson was &thorn;ei wende</L>
