<L>By fynaly &thorn;e kinge axe&thorn; &thorn;e kny&yogh;t</L>
<L>&THORN;e vertue of &thorn;e Coursere and &thorn;e my&yogh;t</L>
<L>And preide hym to telle his gouernance</L>
